      <title>高盛：投资者对欧洲股市上涨感到意外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/investors-surprised-by-european-stock-gains-goldman-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛策略师 Sharon Bell 讨论了欧洲股市的优异表现。Bell 告诉彭博电视台：“很少有投资者预计欧洲会成为表现最好的市场。”她补充道：“美国也存在一些问题，关税可能会导致通胀。”（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-11/investors-surprised-by-european-stock-gains-goldman-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 10:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
